data.description: Welcome home to your serene + classic ranch in beautiful Byers, Colorado! There is no where better start your day than swinging on the front porch while watching the sunrise and listening to the sounds of country living! Just inside, you're met with a dreamy open floorplan where you'll find your spacious kitchen, livingroom, and dining space. There's so much to love here - from the cozy fireplace to the large windows to the high ceilings! With 4 great sized bedrooms, there's plenty of room here for your dream office, gym, or art studio. The tranquil primary suite features those beautiful high ceilings, as well as an attached bathroom with double vanity and gorgeous soaking bathtub. This home makes commuting easy with quick access to I-70, while still enjoying the space + privacy that Byers is known for! The added bonus of Solar Panels, make your electric bill a low dream! Don't forget to check out the barn & chicken coop.....who needs King Soopers for eggs?! You are going to LOVE living here. Call today for your private showing! https://www.virtuance.com/listing/57-e-6th-pl-byers-colorado
